    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我想画一个用户旅程图，记录我典型的工作日流程。整体分成两大块：上班和回家。标题就叫'My working day'吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "journey",
        "title",
        "section"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "好的，两个section分别是'Go to work'和'Go home'。那上班部分具体有哪些步骤？每个步骤需要标注满意度分数和参与角色吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section",
        "Go to work",
        "Go home"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "上班部分有三个环节：先泡茶，满意度5分，我自己做；然后上楼，3分；最后是实际工作，这个只有1分，因为猫老是来打扰，所以角色要加上Cat。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Make tea",
        "Go upstairs",
        "Do work",
        "Me",
        "Cat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加上班section的三个步骤，分数和角色都记下了。现在处理回家的section——'Go home'这边怎么安排？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Go to work",
        "Go home"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "回家就简单多了：下楼，5分；然后坐下休息，也是5分。都是我自己。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Go downstairs",
        "Sit down",
        "Me"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：回家section有两个步骤——'Go downstairs'和'Sit down'，都是5分，角色只有Me。整个图结构是：标题My working day，两个section，上班3步回家2步，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "section",
        "Go to work",
        "Go home",
        "Make tea",
        "Go upstairs",
        "Do work",
        "Go downstairs",
